    [83] 比如，康德指出，“因此，在所有各种声明中，保持诚实(truthful or honest)是一种神圣的、无条件的理性命令法则(commanding law of reason)，并无论如何，承认没有任何私利。”参见，Immanuel Kant, “On a Supposed Right to Lie Because of Philanthropic Concerns,” in Kant, Grounding for the Metaphysics of Morals with On a Supposed Right to Lie Because of Philanthropic Concerns 63, 65 (James W. Ellington trans., 3d ed. 1993).  
